description:
Longford Court and Bell Court are two residential blocks  (high rise and medium rise buildings, Longford is16 floors  and Bell is 4 floors in some parts and 5 floors in others).
Summary of Works to be carried out at Longford Court:•Replacement of roof covering and associated balustrades, upstands and gulleys;
•Replacement of all external windows and balcony doors;•Replacement of all bathrooms and associated services and decorations to Barnet Homes specifications;•Replacement of all kitchens and
